  "text": "A third pathway has been identified via the direct and indirect (Chk2) ATM-dependent activation of BRCA1 [CITATION_1] . This protein seems to be important in the surveillance of DNA replication, participating in checkpoint and repair pathways like p95/Nbs. Its failure is commonly referred to as radioresistant DNA synthesis (RDS).",
